287
00:14:18,970 --> 00:14:20,770
My period comes late this month.

288
00:14:21,110 --> 00:14:22,090
Really?

289
00:14:22,350 --> 00:14:23,290
I see.

290
00:14:23,340 --> 00:14:25,340
